Terrible movie. The voice acting wasn't bad, but the story was. It was 
 uncreative, and incredibly predictable, in that it was like seeing inside out or wreck it ralph again with different characters. The whole story had already been played out before. 

The movie was chock full of ads, and outdated pop culture references like the Pineapple pen video and Silento's "watch me".  Not to mention all of the cringe worthy lines such as "put some sauce on that dance burrito" Would not see again.
